OL,3,CDeaf students call for 'safer' puffin
OL,4,Ccrossing outside their school
OL,6,FStudents tell ITV News' Richard
OL,7,FLawrence the new crossing is vital
OL,9,FStudents at a school for people with
OL,10,Fimpaired or no hearing in Devon are
OL,11,Fcalling for a safer road crossing
OL,12,Foutside their academy.
OL,14,FWork to create a standard crossing
OL,15,Foutside the Deaf Academy in Exmouth is
OL,16,Funderway, but pupils say they need an
OL,17,Fupgraded puffin crossing.
