OL,3,CDeaf students call for 'safer' puffin
OL,4,Ccrossing outside their school
OL,6,FUnlike zebra and pelican crossings, a
OL,7,Fpuffin crossing has extra sensors to
OL,8,Fensure the traffic lights don't change
OL,9,Fto red while a pedestrian is crossing.
OL,11,FThe Deaf Academy relocated to the
OL,12,Fformer Rolle College four years ago.
OL,14,FIt is located near a blind corner on a
OL,15,Froad which can be very busy at rush
OL,16,Fhour.
