OL,3,CDeaf students call for 'safer' puffin
OL,4,Ccrossing outside their school
OL,6,FClaire Quick is part of the leadership
OL,7,Fteam at the college.
OL,9,FShe told ITV News West Country: "Deaf
OL,10,Fpeople need longer to cross the road
OL,11,Fand time to react so it is really
OL,12,Fimportant."
OL,14,FShe says it has taken time to talk
OL,15,Fthrough the right option with the
OL,16,Fcouncil but she is grateful that the
OL,17,Flocal authority is paying more than
OL,18,Fhalf the bill.
